{"article_id":"YXRMYlwhjHEEMfpV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Bolivia 's president says","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"he is willing to grant Snowden asylum","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"The U.S. intelligence leaker has been holed up at the Moscow airport","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Two weeks after arriving at Moscow 's Sheremetyevo International Airport","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and essentially becoming a man without a country ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Edward Snowden finally has some options .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"A trio of left-leaning Latin American nations to varying degrees say","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"they would welcome the U.S. intelligence leaker in their country .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Venezuela and Bolivia have offered asylum to Snowden","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and Nicaragua is willing to consider it .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Bolivian President Evo Morales ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"who became part of the saga","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"when his presidential plane was denied permission","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"to enter the airspace of several European countries amid a rumor about Snowden ,","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"his country is `` willing to give asylum . ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"A day earlier , Venezuelan state media reported","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that President Nicolas Maduro had offered Snowden asylum .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The reports came","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"shortly after Nicaraguan President Daniel Ortega said","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he would grant Snowden asylum in his country `` if the circumstances permit . ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Wanted by the United States ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Snowden had faced a string of rejections to asylum bids","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"he placed","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to numerous countries .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The Latin American countries were the first","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to respond in the positive .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The asylum offers could provide Snowden a chance","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to evade U.S. authorities ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"though it is unclear how he would get to Venezuela or the other countries .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Snowden 's exit from Russia , however , would provide relief to authorities there ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who appeared to grow weary of the American 's presence at the airport .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Alexei Pushkov , head of the lower Russian legislative body DUMA , recommended","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Snowden leave the airport ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"where he has been holed up since June 23 ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"when he arrived from Hong Kong .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"`` Sanctuary for Snowden in Venezuela would be the best solution , ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Pushkov tweeted Saturday .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"`` He ca n't live in at Sheremetyevo . ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Venezuela 's foreign minister said Saturday","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that it has had no contact with Snowden since its asylum offer Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"according to Reuters .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Meanwhile , an Icelandic lawmaker said","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Snowden would not get citizenship there ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"as he had requested ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"because Iceland 's parliament refused to vote on an asylum proposal","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"before ending its current session .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Birgitta Jonsdottir was among a handful of lawmakers","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"who put forward a bill Thursday","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"urging Parliament to process Snowden 's request .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"She said Friday","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"that the speaker of the house refused to put the bill on the agenda","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and the majority in parliament refused to allow a voice vote on it .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Reports :","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Venezuela offers to take leaker","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Reports :","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Venezuela offers to take leaker","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"00:55","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Exploring Snowden 's airport transit zone","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Exploring Snowden 's airport transit zone 01:42","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Snowden 's name used","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"to sell lingerie","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Snowden 's name used to sell lingerie","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"02:10","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Snowden remains a headache for Putin","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Snowden remains a headache for Putin 02:12","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"`` So it is with great grief I have to announce","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that Snowden will not be getting any form of shelter in Iceland","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"because the current government does n't even have enough spine","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"for the Parliament","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"to discuss Snowden 's request , ''","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Jonsdottir wrote on her blog","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"She praised Snowden ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"who has acknowledged leaking classified documents about U.S. surveillance programs","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and faces espionage charges in the United States .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Besides Iceland , he has applied for asylum in 20 other countries .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"`` I and many others regard him as a hero","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and have deep respect for him","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"for he has taken great personal risk","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"in order to inform the rest of us","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"about how those in power have lost control of their powerlust","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"and violated their own constitutions against their own citizens , ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Jonsdottir wrote .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"`` Mr. Snowden your courage has been noted","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and there are millions of people from all backgrounds","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"who honor the risks","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"you have taken for us","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"and we will stand tall with you . ''","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Bolivia 's position on asylum follows outrage","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"expressed by its president over his sidetracked trip from Russia to Bolivia this week .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Several European countries refused to allow Morales ' plane through their airspace Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"because of suspicions","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Snowden was aboard .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"With no clear path home available ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"the flight crew made an emergency landing in Vienna , Austria ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"where authorities confirmed","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Snowden was not a passenger .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Bolivia 's asylum offer is a `` fair protest '' to the incident ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"which involved Portugal , Italy , France and Spain ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Morales said .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"Spain has said","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"it did not restrict its airspace during that flight .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"He put the blame squarely on the United States for the incident .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"`` Message to the Americans :","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"The empire and its servants will never be able to intimidate or scare us , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Morales told supporters at El Alto International Airport outside La Paz ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"where he arrived late Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"`` European countries need to liberate themselves from the imperialism of the Americans . ''","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Morales said","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"officials should analyze","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"whether to shut the U.S. Embassy in his country .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"`` Without the United States , ''","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` we are better politically and democratically . ''","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Ecuadorian President Rafael Correa joined Morales","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"in criticizing the United States ' role in the situation ,","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"and Venezuela 's Maduro blamed the CIA","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"for pressuring the European governments to refuse to grant the plane passage .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":261,"left":134,"right":260,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":0,"right":133,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":132,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":183,"right":259,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":172,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":151,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":136,"right":150,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":136,"left":135,"right":6